{
    "name": "Saintly Knight",
    "type": "npc",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Tactics",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>Before Combat </b>The paladin casts <i>resist energy </i>(fire) unless he expects damage from a different energy type. He applies <i>silversheen </i>to his weapon if he expects to fight devils or lycanthropes.<br/><b>During Combat </b>The paladin uses Ride-By Attack and Spirited Charge, preferring to attack the opposing leader. When on foot, he uses his mace. If facing a powerful foe, he drinks his potions.<br/><b>Base Statistics </b>Without <i>resist energy</i>, the paladin\u2019s statistics are <b>Resist </b>none."
        },
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "html": "A saintly knight accomplishes great acts with his indomitable spirit and martial prowess."
        }
    ],
